               <p>NINTH DAY. SATURDAY, SEPTEMBER 22.</p>
               <p>Third Middlesex Jury - before Mr. Recorder.</p>
               <p>1979. 
               <persName id="t18270913-392-defend2749" type="defendantName">
                  THOMAS 
                  HARDING
               <interp inst="t18270913-392-defend2749" type="surname" value="HARDING"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18270913-392-defend2749" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>
